              ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资信息</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1/rsnyzx/ALL.htm\">ALL</a>\n\n                ›  \n                <a href=\"\">正文</a>\n</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"clearfix \">\n                             <ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\"><li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szdw/szxx1.htm\">师资信息</a></li>\n                    \n<li><a href=\"../../szdw/ltxjs.htm\">离退休教师</a></li>\n                    \n</ul>\n            </div>\n        </div> </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n                 <ul class=\"banner-ul pull-right tabs-ul clearfix wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\"></ul>\n        </div>\n      \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/jquery/jquery-latest.min.js\"></script>\n <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/4/91/4B/9624622921E3153CE014E1EE436_276EE4FB_31CE3.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>罗忠敬</a>教授</div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                        \n                        <p>电子邮箱：cklaw@princeton.edu</p>\n                        <p>通讯地址：北京市海淀区清华大学李兆基科技大楼B-535室</p>\n                        <p>邮编：100084</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"sz\"><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"con\"><p>1973 工程物理博士，美国加州大学圣地亚哥分校</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">1970 航天科学硕士， 加拿大多伦多大学</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">1968 物理学学士， 加拿大阿尔伯塔大学</span></span></span></p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">工作经历</div><div class=\"con\"><p>Princeton University, Department of Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering (1988-)</p>\n<p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n<p>Robert H. Goddard Professor (1995-)</p>\n<p>Professor (1988-1995)</p>\n<p>Associate Chair (1996-1998)</p>\n<p>University of California at Davis, Department of Mechanical Engineering (1984-1988)</p>\n<p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n<p>Professor (Step VI, 1987-88; Step V, 1984-87)</p>\n<p>Northwestern University, Department of Mechanical and Nuclear Engineering (1976-1984)</p>\n<p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n<p>Professor (1981-84)</p>\n<p>Associate Professor (1976-81)</p>\n<p>Princeton University, Department of Aerospace and Mechanical Sciences (1975-1976)</p>\n<p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n<p>Member of Professional Research Staff</p>\n<p>General Motors Research Laboratories (1973-1975)</p>\n<p><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n<p>Associate Senior Research Engineer</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">其他职务</div><div class=\"con\"><p>美国能源部燃烧能源前沿研究中心主任，清华大学燃烧能源中心荣誉主任，国际燃烧学会前主席</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究领域与兴趣</div><div class=\"con\"><p>1. 燃烧理论和燃烧化学；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 层流和湍流火焰动力学和结构特性；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 液滴和颗粒的动力学及气化过程；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4. 代用燃料和生物燃料利用；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5. 燃烧污染物的形成和消除；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6. 天体物理中燃烧现象。</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"con\"><p>美国人文与科学院院士，美国工程院院士<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">曾获多个具代表性的组织，包括美国航空航天学会、美国机械工程师学会、美国工程教育学会及燃烧学会等颁发的多项杰出科研奖、教学奖及论文奖；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2008年被路透社誉为能源燃料界最常被引述作者；<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2000年获得加州大学圣地亚哥分校杰出校友奖，<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap-mode: wrap; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2007年获得香港理工大学杰出校友奖</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">发明专利与著作</div><div class=\"con\"><p>· \"Diazido Alkanes and Diazido Alkanols as Combustion Modifiers for Liquid Hydrocarbon Ramjet Fuels;\" Inventors: R. S. Miller, R. M. Moriarty and C. K. Law; U.S. Patent No. 4,741,742; Date of Patent: May 3, 1988.</p>\n<p>· Chung K. Law, Combustion Physics, Cambridge University Press, 2006.</p></div></div><div class=\"sz20250402\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">期刊文章</div><div class=\"con\"><p>已合作发表国际期刊论文400多篇，论文总引用达7000余次，H指数高达47。</p>\n<p>并于2000年被国际文献资料库「ISI知识网络」誉为工程界中全球最常被引述的百名科学家之一。</p></div></div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    \n\n</form>\n\n    </div>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  <div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container clearfix\">\n     <div class=\"footer-l\">\n              <div class=\"footer-logo\">    \n    <a href=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wbimage&quot;, 1692924305, 59340)\"><img src=\"../../images/dblogo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"imgInline\"></a>\n</div>\n            <div class=\"footer-copyright f16\">\n                <!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>地址：北京市海淀区清华园1号 100084，电话：010-62782508</p><p>Copyright © 2024 清华大学 All Rights Reserved</p>\n            </div>\n\n      </div> \n      \n     